Set proper file permissions in Dockerfile:
RUN chmod 755 /docker-entrypoint.sh && \ chmod 755 /usr/local/bin/integrity-check.sh && \ chmod 644 /etc/java-21-openjdk/security/java.security && \ find /opt/wolfssl-fips/bin -name "*.class" -exec chmod 644 {} \;
Rebuild image with correct permissions.
